PT.EMERSON NETWORK POWER INDONESIA
Emerson Network Power, a business of Emerson (NYSE:EMR), is the global leader in enabling Business-Critical Continuity™ from grid to chip for telecommunication networks, data centers, health care and industrial facilities. Emerson Network Power provides innovative solutions and expertise in areas including AC and DC power and precision cooling systems, embedded computing and power, integrated racks and enclosures, power switching and controls, monitoring, and connectivity. All solutions are supported globally by local Emerson Network Power service technicians. Learn more about Emerson Network Power products and services at .
Customer Service Engineer - Air
Job DescriptionProvide field service support on precision air-conditioning system (maintenance, testing & commissioning, troubleshooting & repair).Build close working relationship with customers and suppliers.Provide quality service and timely follow-up with customers.Provide recommendation and quotation for repair or parts replacement work.Timely report submission.Plan and schedule task assigned by supervisor or manager.Job RequirementsCandidate must possess at least a Bachelor's/College Degree in Mechanical Engineering or equivalent. With extensive knowledge and exposure in HVAC. Possess relevant working experience in air-conditioning companies or equivalent. Proficient in handling technical and service issues.At least 3 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.Good communication skills (oral/written).
